FBIS4-14160 "drnes082_k_94005" FBIS-NES-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 IRAQ PKK Fighters Cut Power in al-Jazirah PKK Fighters Cut Power in al-Jazirah JN2704170394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan in Arabic 1530 GMT 27 Apr 94 JN2704170394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan Arabic BFN [Text] On the night of 24-25 April, an armed group belonging to the PKK [Kurdistan Workers Party] cut off electricity in Dahuk Governorate by destroying an electrical tower near the town of al-Jazirah. This is the second time PKK forces have cut off electric power in the area.
